getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取我的Bug数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYBUGS from zt_bug t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.assignedTo = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取我的Bug数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYTASKS from zt_task t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.assignedTo = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 我的待办数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) as MYTODOCNT from zt_todo t1 where t1.cycle = '0' and t1.account = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取我的需求数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t1.id) AS MYSTORYS from zt_story t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and t1.assignedTo = ?
